This has to be one of the all-time best B-rated sci-fi flicks!  Sure, the swords never get blood on them!  Sure, their clothes never get torn no matter how much running through the woods they do!  But this is a fun movie!  Great lines!  And Alex Hyde-White with long auburn hair!  Need I say more?
